title: Complete DC Crisis - 'Flash of two worlds' upto 'Final Crisis'
description:
The complete DC crisis series starting from 'Flash of 2 worlds' going through to the last 'final crisis'. An attempt to collect all the comics, in chronological order, linking them so that you can make some sense of it all.

This will give you a pretty good idea about all the DC events pre new 52 line.

Contains
1. Crisis on Multiple Earths
2. Crisis on Infinite Earths
3. Zero Hour Crisis in Time
4. Crisis Time 5
5. Identity Crisis
6. Infinite Crisis
7. Final Crisis

.............................and everything in between.

Suggest you read the origin stories of all the DC heroes b4 you begin

Enjoy.


PS. Please be patient with the seeds. my connection is slow
